data.description:
Large 2-story home with owner's suite, a den, full bathroom, and another bedroom all situated on the first floor. The 2nd floor offers a large Loft with storage room, another full bathroom as well as 2 other bedrooms for your guests' convenience. Highlights of this home are: a Brand-New Roof, 2019 Air Conditioning system, Granite and solid surface tops through-out, Huge screened in area for yourfamily gatherings or your hot tub, etc., Downstairs is all high level laminate/plank flooring along with tile with upstairs having wall to wall tile, Cul-de-sac lot and more. Located in the premier and secure 24/7 gated and beautiful almost maintenance free community of ''The Villages of Royal Palm'' in the heart of Port Orange where shopping,interstate access, hospitals, Brand new Emergency Room, beach (7-miles away), The library, doctors, schools and 
beaches, and churches are all just a few minutes away from you. 
HOA covers full lawn care/landscaping, yard pest control and sprinkler maintenance, Spectrum Cable TV and Internet, Exterior Paint (once every 6-years), Pressure washing of house (once a year), tennis courts, basketball court, putting green, shuffle board, bocce ball, horse shoes, table tennis, whirl pool, 2 pools (1 heated), fabulous clubhouse with ballroom and caterers kitchen, fitness center, library, billiard, crafts room, office center, monthly calendar with scheduled activities plus large covered patio to enjoy lunch by the pool.
Don't miss out on this beautiful home.
